                            <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0011923&amp;fLockTerm=Diagnostic+imaging%2c+not+elsewhere+classified">Diagnostic imaging, not elsewhere classified</a>
 (88.90), <a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0013516&amp;fLockTerm=Diagnostic+ultrasound+of+heart">Diagnostic ultrasound of heart</a>
 (88.72), <a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0031809&amp;fLockTerm=General+physical+examination">General physical examination</a>
 (89.7), <a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375086&amp;fLockTerm=Hodgkin%27s+disease%2c+unspecified+type%2c+unspecified+site%2c+extranodal+and+solid+organ+sites">Hodgkin&#39;s disease, unspecified type, unspecified site, extranodal and solid organ sites</a>
 (201.90), <a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0029664&amp;fLockTerm=Other+mammography">Other mammography</a>
 (87.37)                    </div>
