, <a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0040130&amp;fLockTerm=Thyroid+Function+Tests">Thyroid Function Tests</a>
, <a href="/web/20180609204955/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0040405&amp;fLockTerm=X-Ray+Computed+Tomography">X-Ray Computed Tomography</a>
