        <li>Chemistry panel </li>
        <li>Thyroid panel </li>
        <li>Lipid profile </li>
    </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Patient education and counseling </li>
</ol></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Major Outcomes Considered</a></h3>
                    <p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
    <li>Utility of radiologic examination in the follow-up of Hodgkin lymphoma </li>
    <li>Positive and negative predictive value of radiologic tests</li>
    <li>Median, failure-free, and overall survival </li>
    <li>Cost-effectiveness of radiologic tests </li>
    <li>Risk of developing relapse of Hodgkin lymphoma, secondary cancers, cardiac disease, stroke, and other complications of treatment </li>
</ul></p>

